data.description: Nestled in the prestigious Stafford at Langtree community, this exquisite home offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience. Featuring 5 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms, this property is designed with an open floor plan, a chef's kitchen, and high ceilings (10' on the main level and 9' upstairs) that enhance its spacious and airy ambiance. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops. Outdoors, you'll find a covered rear patio, a fenced backyard that backs onto undeveloped land, offering unparalleled privacy. The home is upgraded with an enlarged patio made of pavers. The community offers amenities, including a pool with beach entry, a clubhouse, and a recreation area. Located conveniently close to Downtown Mooresville and Davidson. This home is better than new, with est. landscape and immediate availability, eliminating the wait for new construction. Embrace the opportunity to reside in this exceptional home, where luxury meets the comfort of everyday living. Agent is also the Seller.
